Folder to keep your persistent config files

Setup Instructions:

1. Clone the Repository, then run:
2. cp config.TEMPLATE.inc.php ojs.config.inc.php
3. Then run the docker compose file
4. To be sure your volumes have the right permissions run:
   i. sudo chown 100:101 ./volumes -R
   ii. sudo chown 999:999 ./volumes/db -R
